<div class="demo-test-area--wrapper">
  <div class="demo-test-area--title">
    <div class="demo-test-area--title-main">glimmer-chat-window demo</div>
    <div class="demo-test-area--title-sub">made by Rajasegar</div>
  </div>
  <form class="demo-test-area" onsubmit={{ action handleSubmit }}>
    <div class="demo-test-area--preamble">Test the chat window by sending a message:</div>
    <textarea
      class="demo-test-area--text"
      placeholder="Write a test message...."
    />
    <button class="demo-test-area--button"> Send Message! </button>
  </form>
  <p class="demo-test-area--info">
    glimmer-live-chat is a chat window that allows you to build and add custom live chat to your sites.
    It includes only the glimmer chat widget. There is no backend, and no communication system baked in.
    <br />
    <br/>
    For instructions on how to use glimmer-chat-window click <a href="https://github.com/rajasegar/glimmer-live-chat">here</a>.
  </p>
</div>
